onHandleIntent(Intent) - Method in class de.awi.floenavigation.aismessages.AISDecodingService
This function splits the received packet on the basis of comma and sends the data to be decoded to the AIVDM class After the payload is decoded the required parameters are stored into the corrsponding tables of the internal local database If the received mmsi is present in the DatabaseHelper.stationListTable the decoded payload along with the mmsi is stored in DatabaseHelper.fixedStationTable else it is stored in DatabaseHelper.mobileStationTable If there is error in any SQLite Database instructions, the exceptions are handled using try catch exception handlers and appropriate log messages are added.
onHandleIntent(Intent) - Method in class de.awi.floenavigation.network.NetworkService
 
onHandleIntent(Intent) - Method in class de.awi.floenavigation.services.AlphaCalculationService
This method is invoked on the worker thread AlphaCalculationService.timer is initialized with a Timer task to run every 10000 msecs In the task for each mobile station read from the internal local database DatabaseHelper.mobileStationTable AlphaCalculationService.distance, AlphaCalculationService.alpha, AlphaCalculationService.stationX and AlphaCalculationService.stationY are calculated and stored in the DatabaseHelper.mobileStationTable table
onHandleIntent(Intent) - Method in class de.awi.floenavigation.services.AngleCalculationService
